# Raw SQL Executor Application with Ecto

This Elixir application demonstrates how to execute raw SQL queries using `Ecto.Adapters.SQL.query()`. It covers both secure parameter binding (recommended) and the **highly insecure** method of string interpolation (to show what *not* to do with user input).

